Includes records for which Long Beach was recorded on the death certificate as the decedents city of residence.  Duplicate records due to revisions to the death certificate are not included.  ICD-10 codes were not included in the dataset; algorithms were written to match key words from cause of death to the corresponding ICD-10 diagnosis.
Notes: Deaths for which cause was listed as deferred for review by a coroner or for which cause was missing are not included.  Counts from which rates are derived are subject to change due to late reporting or revisions to the cause of death.

Includes records for which Long Beach was recorded on the death certificate as the decedents city of residence.  Duplicate records due to revisions to the death certificate are not included.  ICD-10 codes were not included in the dataset; algorithms were written to match key words from cause of death to the corresponding ICD-10 diagnosis.
Notes: Deaths for which cause was listed as deferred for review by a coroner or for which cause was missing are not included.  Counts from which rates are derived are subject to change due to late reporting or revisions to the cause of death.
